cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and semantic role labeling. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new method for modeling predicate-argument thematic fit judgments using a distributional approach. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with computational models of semantics. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper involves computational methods and feature extraction.
